{"tid":1108263,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"沒事兒之幾百次實時報倉百發百中證明區","createTime":"2019-04-15T23:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T09:00:17.000Z","uid":52911,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"19e4ba339e47c213955b5f1977f7a246c109c89a","tid":1108263,"uid":52911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:52:20.000Z","msg":"沒事兒<br />\n大家都熟悉嘅名字<br />\n過去一年一直聲稱自己實時報倉超過幾百次<br />\n全部百發百中 幫左百鳩幾位巴打賺錢<br />\n但每次叫佢比證明 佢會有幾個回應<br />\n1）佢無必要證明<br />\n2）入hi淡友post問是但一個巴打都知道<br />\n3）有心人要搵一定搵到<br />\n4）個個都抹黑佢<br />\n我決定做佢口中嘅有心人<br />\n但我能力低, 搵左好耐都搵唔到佢所謂嘅百發百中實時報倉<br />\n所以開post希望各位可以幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我目標只係搵到佢口中幾百次報倉嘅1/10 <br />\n只要有20個證明 <br />\n我會開post公開同沒事兒道歉 以後唔再狙擊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d197bf4eda6056c420c9bf6daa81e4fc7cb67bf4","tid":1108263,"uid":52911,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5O9ykN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5O9ykN.jpg&h=3f18e2d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補圖<br />\n沒事兒最新回應"},{"pid":"a60b880ccd4a5b79418baca02869f4dfd79d3fb9","tid":1108263,"uid":1654,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:55:21.000Z","msg":"有就實搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇就難講d"},{"pid":"a675f210a058d4043795f55abe581c166a36515d","tid":1108263,"uid":52911,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:56:45.000Z","msg":"畀佢幫過而賺錢嘅百鳩幾位巴打<br />\n呢一年來都無見你哋出現過<br />\n希望你哋幫幫沒事兒<br />\n只要有1/5嘅人出黎幫手<br />\n就證明到沒事兒唔係鳩吹<br />\n請幫幫幫你哋賺錢嘅大恩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43698b9fbc0d1facaa287cca1a40e3689f7fddf","tid":1108263,"uid":195998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:57:22.000Z","msg":"👍👍👍😱😱😱"},{"pid":"6a7f4e09fe52231dd882e1591d4482a4d791db5f","tid":1108263,"uid":52911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a60b880ccd4a5b79418baca02869f4dfd79d3fb9","tid":1108263,"uid":1654,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:55:21.000Z","msg":"有就實搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇就難講d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:59:27.000Z","msg":"我淨係搵到佢笑鳩人上車 笑鳩人住公屋 同埋起人底爆人私隱啲post<br />\n實時報倉就未搵到"},{"pid":"6181bbc4f7468bc0ad43adfc12f958d8b6c5bc3a","tid":1108263,"uid":195998,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T00:01:11.000Z","msg":"我有次屌佢買跌但即升<br />\n<br />\n之後佢話自己一早放左 賺左少少 即係數格仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲話自己係WhatsApp 到提大家<br />\n<br />\n但係淡友post 無人知道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果時上年7 8 月到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0536e57d79980bad10b69f4c1a0e6186ef53436b","tid":1108263,"uid":52911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T00:03:48.000Z","msg":"佢話幾百個實時報倉唔難搵<br />\n我就畀一星期時間大家一齊搵<br />\n或者等沒事兒自己貼倉 但佢自己貼嘅話我要佢全數貼<br />\n一星期後都無人證明到 沒事兒又唔自貼倉<br />\n呢倉遊戲就完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cfd399edaec4f048cd25d1e2718d5185fd2c1b0","tid":1108263,"uid":52911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T00:04:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢話幾百個實時報倉唔難搵<br />\n我就畀一星期時間大家一齊搵<br />\n或者等沒事兒自己貼倉 但佢自己貼嘅話我要佢全數貼<br />\n一星期後都無人證明到 沒事兒又唔自貼倉<br />\n呢個遊戲就完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b7dd847a0a02a2d0ff0b2064fac4ccfe3d017692","tid":1108263,"uid":52911,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6181bbc4f746