邏輯都無<br />\n<br />\n就係以上兩點已經知道佢有幾多料到<br />\n<br />\n其實樓主都唔需要花時間係呢啲人身上<br />\n<br />\n投資成功與否，係自己既事<br />\n而家資訊咁發達既年代，每日咁多人吹噓自己，個個都查咪好唔得閒，信與否未必一定要實證，單純邏輯推理及分析就夠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我都係當得閒撚下狗咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0090a868d7bae4bff5bd72d83972938ba76bff7","tid":1108263,"uid":52911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"喂大佬 幾百個實時報倉都無人畀到出黎<br />\n好難信係真喎沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a180c6c4197280c83c5fe974ed55f15f9f09e174","tid":1108263,"uid":195998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T19:08:10.000Z","msg":"一個都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3158a4db90f3f09d294b1979e2d6a4aceed161c","tid":1108263,"uid":52911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a180c6c4197280c83c5fe974ed55f15f9f09e174","tid":1108263,"uid":195998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T19:08:10.000Z","msg":"一個都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03883b5052d2109c34ff8b6b337ee5937ce5315b","tid":1108263,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:00:17.000Z","msg":"佢應該唔敢再出post"}]}